Comment: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told them it's too early for the Mark I to go to the Smithsonian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mark I has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried contacting it using the JAF, Allied Forces, and public circuits,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've gotten no responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means the pilot's ignoring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he just doesn't know how to use the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is definitely a logical explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash, this beeping is annoying the heck out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about weapons? Do you have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand any of this technical jargon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not as easy as it looks in a cartoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese Armed Forces asserts ownership of that machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Okinawan SDF's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conventional weaponry is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret can clearly see them if they use weapons like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena—Musou gauge full.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impacts of all Goliath missiles have been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for second rou—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just squealed, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do that on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, withdraw for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to withdraw from the fight {\i1}again{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're becoming a babysitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children shouldn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant has to look like a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark I entered the Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... We have to get out of the Zone quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one piloting this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Generation Bleu the only ones that are allowed to fight G-Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secrets can't detect IFOs that are outside the ZOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZOA?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zone Out of Action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within the Zone, Secrets can catch IFOs in the matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to fight without even knowing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please move! The G-Monsters are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're outside the Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we don't initiate on them, we're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't hide again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to fight? Can you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can leave my friend behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm coming along as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the G-Monsters destroy this island, it'll be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The size of a Scub Burst is usually four times the size of the Coral and Secret put together—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay here anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, I'm starting to get a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming. Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lure them all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you do that, I'll get to the big one and take it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, inside the Zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got at least a few dozen seconds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His strategy is plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mark I's strength lies in the machine itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the closer it gets, the more effective it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is whether or not it can do anything significant with just one arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't entrust our fates to a newbie piloting a damaged machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, listen to my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ivica!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let children die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all else fails, we'll use the Triton to shield them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, input the course and countdown for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can use your radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to hear what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be the decoy {\i1}and{\i0} babysit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a pay raise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, I'm sending data over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop quoting comic books!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not quoting comic books... I'm quoting cartoo—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can use Kyrie's cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All IFO designs are derived from the Mark I's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't do anything but mimic it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this explosion is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a possibility that the Scub Coral is emitting harmful particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can confirm that it is safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,civilians may not enter a 3km radius of the Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear? There are harmful particles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Generation Bleu people weren't wearing any masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the Italian stallion to join the race!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Burst calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks just like the real plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them take Ao away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, a woman saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had blue hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Ao is Eureka's son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our company runs a program to raise children like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in junior high already. Let him decide by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Ao is? Please take me to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! I'm Arata Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao is hopeless without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you meet Ao, would you please tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what I'm about to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nirvash safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even children can reach that beach now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rescued me from the sea and now you're doing this... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? I've always wanted to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been just ten years since one could gather trapars here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The development has been amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okinawa's FP ownership count is the highest in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{hh}Get rid of the Allied Forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{hh}Let's get our independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{hh}Give us back the trapars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{hh}Let's get our independence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{hh}Get rid of the Allied Forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want Okinawan control over the Scub Coral!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johanson is the answer if you're seeking the truth of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're independent on paper, but the Allied Forces have their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, our tourism and fishing industry are both dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means things aren't going that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got no place to stay? What are you going to do about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can sleep in my company's dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wanted him to taste your cooking, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful dye-job. It's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd get popular with girls if you had a nice dye-job like his.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister is a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy I met recently works for the intelligence agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you selling Ao out to the Allied Forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He piloted that IFO and now both the JAF and the Allied Forces want him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hand him over, we'd get—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, the food was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a chance to go to America, but now it's gone thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was still a kid, a G-Monster attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the one you're piloting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're landing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here at your workplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is the world's largest trapar mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message for you from your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That giant belongs to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, she piloted the giant to the Scub Burst and never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you pilot the giant, you'll end up like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we don't know anything about what happened to your mother, Eureka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I continue piloting the Nirvash...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps one day, I'll find the path that she followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you let me join Generation Bleu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The targets are the plant coral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the boy and Mark I!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've always had wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings that will carry you away from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Mom's alive, I want to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if I neglected her, Grandpa would get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, I want to come with—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, you should stay and take care of your granny and Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't fight too much with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them if they know of a way to cure your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generation Bleu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're G-Monster specialists, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to know something about your sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything else to give to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allied Forces IFOs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Allied Forces here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the same reason as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably hacked the taxi company and used the car cameras to track him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they came up with the same idea as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Mark I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's being prepared for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are others who also think the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet up with the Triton right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Allied Forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And IFOs have no problem detecting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even last for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generation Bleu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll file an official request for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was here just then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. If you didn't run away from that Doberman, we wouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found a blanket!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the mist, the boy sees a black tower slicing the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new world he faces grants him new encounters as well as doubts,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.83,0:24:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making him wonder the meaning of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka Seven AO, episode five: Tighten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
